CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 21, 1945, pg. 25 reads: "Nuptials - Friends gathered at the home of Mr. and Mrs. Will McQueen last Saturday to celebrate their recent marriage. Shown left to right are Miss Mildred Johnson, Mrs. Carrie L. English, Will McQueen, Randolph English, Mrs. Will McQueen, Mr. and Mrs. Eudell Williams and Miss Elizabeth Johnson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of five women and three men, including left to right; Mildred Johnson, Carrie L. English, Will McQueen, Randolph English, Mrs. Will McQueen, Mr. and Mrs. Eudell Williams, and Elizabeth Johnson, standing behind three tiered cake in domestic interior with striped wallpaper
